---
title: Pinoy-Style Chicken Adobo with Garlic Rice and Green Beans
description: Don't confuse this national dish of the Philippines with its Mexican counterpart. This version relies on soy sauce, vinegar and lots of onions, garlic and peppercorn to make the dish come alive!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-adobo-facon-philippine-f7850c74.jpg
